{
  "stem": "13600.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some kind of improvised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Table, chair, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say in the Cheder would be 12 to 15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my knowledge, [LAUGHTER] no, no, I wouldn't say so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was obligatory, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You accept.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have learned from the very beginning to accept things that cannot be resisted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no choice in that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Democracy didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The word democracy, I learned much later in my life-- choice, democracy, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the garments, that was-- how can I describe it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dark, drab-- it was a ghetto clothing, you know, that it was imposed on Jews hundreds of years ago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So later, they accepted it on their own volition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- that is, that is correct.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or [? wasn't ?] religious-- there were some Jews who didn't wear that, that wore modern clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, of course, quite a number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it was obligatory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't have any other way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes-- sidelocks, you mean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a problem, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Walking in Warsaw with sidelocks was courting danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would say in Warsaw, while I was studying in yeshiva, whenever I went out in the streets, I was kicked or abused-- verbally abused, assaulted.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less-- the exception would be to be in a tolerant surrounding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, kicked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be just-- not bashed up is a bit more, but--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pushed, kicked, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would, I would say so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say that Aborigines here have got a very good life in comparison with our life, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And besides, in Warsaw there was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Jewish part, the part the Jews lived, our life was a ghetto life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were much safer.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
